# ngx_http_waf_module - search-engine / archival crawler User-Agent signatures
#
# $waf_type = crawler. Flag-only: surfaced for the operator, never blocked by
# waf_bot_block. Industry practice treats 'spider' as a synonym for crawler
# (it is only a UA token), so spider-style bots live here -- there is no
# separate spider category. One case-insensitive PCRE2 fragment per line.
#
# NEVER add a bare 'bot', 'spider' or 'crawl' token here: they false-positive
# on countless legitimate and AI agents. Use the distinctive product token.
#
# Sources: monperrus/crawler-user-agents, Matomo bots.yml.

Googlebot
bingbot
Slurp
Baiduspider
YandexBot
DuckDuckBot
Applebot
Sogou
PetalBot
SeznamBot
archive\.org_bot
heritrix
